{"lemma":"نَوّاسُ","slug":"نَوّاسُ","root":"ن.#.س","root_slug":"ن-_-س","root_link":"/words/roots/ن-_-س","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n40746","n40748"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%86%D9%8E%D9%88%D9%91%D8%A7%D8%B3%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n40746","headword_ar":"نُوَاسٌ","root":"nws","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lock of hair such as is called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*uw^aAbap","text_ar":"ذُوَابَة"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that moves to and fro:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, in explanation of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*uw nuwaAsK","text_ar":"ذُو نُوَاسٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"the name of a king of El-Yemen:) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nuwaAsapN","text_ar":"نُوَاسَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"has this signification: (A:) [the former, therefore, is a coll. gen. n., and this is indicated in the S; and the latter is its n. un.:] and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nawasaAtN","text_ar":"نَوَسَاتٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*awaAy^ibu","text_ar":"ذَوَايِبُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*uw^aAbapN","text_ar":"ذُوَابَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] because they move about much. (TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"What hangs to the roof,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, A, &c. [a signification assigned in the K to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naAsN","text_ar":"نَاسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", probably through the careless omission of the word"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aln~uwaAsu","text_ar":"النُّوَاسُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"by an early transcriber,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"consisting of smoke,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA,) [or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"soot,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"&c."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,) The word in the T and O, as well as in the A [and M], is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nuwaAsN","text_ar":"نُوَاسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b3-  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"web"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a spider: because of its fluttering. (M.)"}],"source_refs":["A","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n40748","headword_ar":"نَوَّاسٌ","root":"nws","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", applied to man, (S,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Quivering"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muDoTaribN","text_ar":"مُضْطَرِبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"),"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and flaccid,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"flabby."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K.)"}],"source_refs":["S"]}]}}